Please accept the following letter.  The signatories are two of five co-aut=
hors on a paper published December 6, 2013 in PLOS ONE.  Tamar Haspel's pie=
ce in the "Health Section" of today's paper addressed, and challenged some =
of our findings.  We had several positive and professional exchanges with T=
